463
00:32:31,820 --> 00:32:34,060
What's your reason for taking photos here?

464
00:32:34,060 --> 00:32:35,670
Tell me. I want to know.

465
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,060
I was just curious,

466
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:40,320
so Nana brought me here to look around.

467
00:32:43,260 --> 00:32:44,790
But after looking around,

468
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:48,500
I'm not that impressed.
There's nothing special.

469
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,880
Then tell me,

470
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:52,540
