492
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:03,350
A light clutch is easy to operate.

493
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:05,300
Faster coupling reduces time loss.

494
00:34:05,300 --> 00:34:07,390
This, in turn,
leads to better performance.

495
00:34:07,390 --> 00:34:09,230
It's a simple principle.

496
00:34:11,770 --> 00:34:13,480
I also drove a car a few days ago.

497
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:16,810
