It was really hard to control.

498
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:20,790
Was it a pickup truck?

499
00:34:21,460 --> 00:34:22,320
How do you know?

500
00:34:22,750 --> 00:34:25,350
The stiff clutch is caused by
its hard springs.

501
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:27,500
It enables a quick connection

502
00:34:27,830 --> 00:34:30,909
