505
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:38,480
Stomping on it to shift is too rude.

506
00:34:40,500 --> 00:34:41,760
You shift quickly too,

507
00:34:41,870 --> 00:34:43,469
but your clutch isn't stiff.

508
00:34:44,010 --> 00:34:47,139
Every car has its own performance balance.

509
00:34:47,389 --> 00:34:48,250
How to modify it

510
00:34:48,449 --> 00:34:50,449
depends on the owner's preference.

511
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:52,100
